output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. CMF Number: No CMF number is present, but this isn't decisive.
2. Refers to candidate (Art 36.7.a): - Directly mentions George Simion, who is a presidential candidate - Also promotes AUR and the poster's own parliamentary candidacy
3. Addresses wide population (Art 36.7.b): - This is a paid Facebook advertisement - Reached between 70,000-79,999 impressions - Clearly intended for mass distribution
4. Electoral objective (Art 36.7.c): - The post has dual purposes: * Promotes parliamentary candidacy (which is still allowed) * References and endorses George Simion's "plan" (presidential candidate)
5. Journalism/Personal Opinion: - This is clearly campaign material, not journalism - Structured as a political advertisement - Paid distribution confirms promotional nature
The post is problematic because while parliamentary campaign is still allowed, it includes promotion of George Simion, a presidential candidate, after the presidential campaign period has ended.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This constitutes electoral propaganda because: 1. It's a paid advertisement reaching a large audience 2. It explicitly promotes George Simion's vision and plan 3. It links parliamentary candidacy with presidential candidate's agenda 4. Uses significant financial resources (600-699 RON) for distribution
conclusion.message-for-police: UNIWORLD - MEDIA SRL și Doina Mihăilescu, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin difuzarea unui material de propagandă electorală (ID postare Facebook: 1139425044849387) care promovează candidatul prezidențial George Simion după încheierea perioadei de campanie electorală. Materialul, difuzat după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, face referire directă la "planul lui George Simion" și exprimă susținerea pentru acesta, constituind astfel propagandă electorală continuată după încheierea campaniei. Impactul a fost semnificativ, postarea având între 70.000-79.999 de afișări, fiind sponsorizată cu suma de 600-699 RON.
